{
  "stem": "25209.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I went to see a-- I made a couple of Jewish girlfriends.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I went to see a rabbi because I wanted-- I was very anti-God.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I said, said to the rabbi, [LAUGHS] you prove to me there is a God.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he said, here, take these books and read them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I said, no, I've read enough books.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You prove to me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he said, sorry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that was the last time I spoke to a rabbi except for when I got married.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were married in a, in a synagogue.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But yeah, so there were no answers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I didn't even have the questions.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I just had fury.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So yeah, that's how that went.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I liked Prague.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I really identified Prague as my home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I knew that Prague was my home and that, you know, after 40 years, 30 years, in Australia, I didn't really know that I had any more feelings for over there.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then in '68 when, when Dubcek tried to change things, and we were watching things on television or whatever, and I got so upset.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went to all these meetings and demonstrations.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's how I realized that I was still Czech-- Czech, Jewish, Australian, Russian, whatever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, well, my aunt and uncle were here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They got out in '39 or '38-- or they were here forever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were here, so that's how we, we got the visa, or I don't know-- something that's necessary.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there was nothing to stop us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was still all normal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The, the, the communists weren't, weren't in it yet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We just said, we want to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they said, OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that's a story in itself.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
